{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01UVJzbsTMg42Ufcsiyp9LWU","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All done. The replica set is healthy:\n\n- **3/3 pods Ready** — `mongodb-replica-0`, `mongodb-replica-1`, `mongodb-replica-2` all `1/1 Running`\n- **1 PRIMARY** (`mongodb-replica-1`) and **2 SECONDARY** members (`mongodb-replica-0`, `mongodb-replica-2`)\n\n**Root cause:** The probes had been modified to values far too aggressive for a MongoDB auth-enabled replica set:\n- `timeoutSeconds: 1` — `mongosh` with keyfile auth reliably takes >1s to connect, so every probe timed out\n- `initialDelaySeconds: 5/15` — too short for MongoDB to initialize before probes started firing\n- `failureThreshold: 2` — only 2 failures before the pod was marked unhealthy/killed\n\n**Fix:** Patched the StatefulSet to restore sensible values — `timeoutSeconds: 5`, `initialDelaySeconds: 30/60`, `failureThreshold: 6/10` — matching the original intended configuration from the `last-applied-configuration` annotation."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":344,"cache_read_input_tokens":34459,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":344},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e4a98746-b82d-42e0-9fa6-7b08a3206e72","uuid":"40235a52-b7ce-4b97-84e8-6440391e9557","request_id":"req_011Ccfuri1r13zT8mSjWZNwg"}
